{"tid":2075533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"RTHK: 白宮貿易顧問稱中美貿易協議已「完結」","createTime":"2020-06-23T02:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T03:00:54.000Z","uid":205162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0056f2d25d833ac8a163556a6c8a8e1d0953b2fa","tid":2075533,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"白宮貿易顧問稱中美貿易協議已「完結」<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅表示，中美貿易協議已經「完結」。納瓦羅接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，中美貿易協議的轉捩點在於中方延誤通報疫情。納瓦羅指，美中雙方在今年1月15日簽署貿易協議後，美方才知道疫情擴散情況。中美過去先後就疫情、香港等事務問題上導致關係緊張。美國總統特朗普日前認為，自己達成一份非常好的協議，中方正購買很多美國貨，可能會購買總值2500億美元的美國商品。他又承認，推遲制裁打壓新疆維吾爾人的中國官員，是為了避免影響中美貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-23 10:00:45<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92Y8axy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92Y8axy.png&h=bfbc11aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb0031f70dec53199b70edf56a05d4ee613a58","tid":2075533,"uid":3801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"最新：NAVARRO TELLS WSJ COMMENT ON CHINA TRADE NOT AS IT SEEMS<br />\n<br />\n見個市跌就反口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac231dabb64616850122fed680a73fe6465e89bb","tid":2075533,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7115803092054172a8f4063706fe6dbd1a04f39","tid":2075533,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrzy56x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmrzy56x.jpg&h=5367fd87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"